cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the technical aspects of automated driving systems, which involves robotics and control systems. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as perception is one of the core functions of ADSs and involves computer vision techniques. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as ADSs heavily rely on AI techniques for decision-making and planning. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper discusses the high-level system architectures and control systems involved in ADSs. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as machine learning techniques are used in various aspects of ADSs, such as perception and decision-making.
